sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Device as Demo.DeviceCode
    participant OpenId as OpenIdController
    participant DeviceSvc as DeviceAuthorizationService
    participant DeviceRepo as DeviceAuthorizationRepository
    participant Token as TokenController
    participant TokenSvc as TokenService

    Device->>OpenId: POST /connect/deviceauthorization
    OpenId->>DeviceSvc: StartAsync
    DeviceSvc->>DeviceRepo: AddAsync(device_authorization)
    DeviceRepo-->>DeviceSvc: 持久化 device_code / user_code
    DeviceSvc-->>OpenId: 返回 verification_uri / user_code
    OpenId-->>Device: device_code 响应

    loop 轮询
        Device->>Token: POST /connect/token<br/>grant_type=device_code
        Token->>DeviceSvc: PollAsync
        DeviceSvc->>DeviceRepo: FindByDeviceCodeAsync + UpdateAsync
        alt 用户未授权
            DeviceSvc-->>Token: authorization_pending / slow_down
            Token-->>Device: 错误响应
        else 用户已授权
            DeviceSvc-->>Token: user_id / client_id / scope
            Token->>TokenSvc: IssueAccessTokenWithMetadataAsync
            Token->>TokenSvc: IssueRefreshTokenAsync
            Token-->>Device: access_token + refresh_token
        end
    end
